{"tid":1695412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解都未正式有一個罷工活動出現 就已經咁多人屌人唔肯罷？","createTime":"2019-11-05T15:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T17:35:34.000Z","uid":258287,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd0669ff2c107425ee2c61c4c30e98c92cc3dea","tid":1695412,"uid":258287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"日日上連登都見到一大班屌人唔肯罷工，但明明自從9月之後都再冇正式嘅罷工活動出現，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>佢地又知香港人一定唔肯罷？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無可否認全民長期罷工一定係最大春袋而且贏撚硬，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但正正就係因為呢招咁撚勁(直頭無敵)，所以發動條件先會咁難！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你地打機幾撚時見過秒全圖嘅大技係可以話放就放仲要連住放架？<br />\n<br />\n仲有成日係度屌人第二日照常返工，我想講，我weekend發夢勇武完又攰又痛，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期一係就係繼續返工啊，</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔撚係&ldquo;照常&rdquo;囉！</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢4個幾月以黎我未撚試過一日係&ldquo;照常返工&rdquo;啊！</span></span></strong>日日返工到公司乜柒都做唔掂，凈係識上連登同睇新聞，零社交兼抑鬱，見到手足受傷/死...心up到係公司趴低扮訓係度喊...<br />\n<br />\n我自己都等緊全民大罷工嘅時機，只要發動到呢招，我地贏撚硬！所以求下各位連登嘅手足，俾啲耐性，既然已經有人組織緊，請相信香港人，唔好再屌啦！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地越屌只會令罷工呢招更難發動！不如趁而家呼籲多啲身邊人做好罷工嘅準備啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n煲底見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9a60113d77faccac0d8932f69a8c7c7a80131bf1","tid":1695412,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"11月9日：7區開花！香港人反抗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689356\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34191b85d917e8923352ad2c89349132685b1f1a","tid":1695412,"uid":258287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4c99f7587e9aaa8892c549d1fe418eb0d4c0e90f","tid":1695412,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"四個幾月乜都做唔掂仲未被炒？"},{"pid":"878295bc77e769606230ca842bde48ebbb84b511","tid":1695412,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"認同 呢招明明係大技<br />\n氣都未儲 成班剩係識今日講聽日罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪搞到每次都咁多悔氣撚出黎囉"},{"pid":"b13c5704f5f1987a7488568f0b92317f4e3fdd2a","tid":1695412,"uid":258287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c99f7587e9aaa8892c549d1fe418eb0d4c0e90f","tid":1695412,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"四個幾月乜都做唔掂仲未被炒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"feel就炒架啦，我都唔旨在了，凈係想香港人贏到"},{"pid":"b7f2039a4ba4b1951f098d073d34b9ccbfd59814","tid":1695412,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d733ad633869ef1ddfa8e062880322cc16d57a0","tid":1695412,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:33:44.000Z","msg":"樓主老闆會唔會太好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd58debb67834932d8397351489032e0a4b8197","tid":1695412,"uid":258287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878295bc77e769606230ca842bde48ebbb84b511","tid":1695412,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"認同 呢招明明係大技<br />\n氣都未儲 成班剩係識今日講聽日罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪搞到每次都咁多悔氣撚出黎囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"無錯，當我唔覺得佢地係鬼，只係大